    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you say \"not a permanent state,\" but what if it is? i feel like i've hit a limit. like there's a version of a person that's whole and healthy and i just don't have the parts for that anymore. i've been through so much that i think i'm just... beyond repair. it feels more like an objective fact than just a feeling.",
